{
  "video_id": "OEydHbngSz0",
  "title": "You don't have to be an expert to solve big problems | Tapiwa Chiwewe",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12849.0,
      "end_time": 16706.0,
      "text": "One winter morning, a couple of years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16730.0,
      "end_time": 19705.0,
      "text": "I was driving to work in Johannesburg, South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19729.0,
      "end_time": 22300.0,
      "text": "and noticed a haze hanging over the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22895.0,
      "end_time": 24990.0,
      "text": "I make that drive on most days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25140.0,
      "end_time": 27887.0,
      "text": "so it was unusual that I hadn&#39;t noticed this before."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28559.0,
      "end_time": 31648.0,
      "text": "Johannesburg is known for its distinctive skyline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31672.0,
      "end_time": 33489.0,
      "text": "which I could barely see that morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34322.0,
      "end_time": 38843.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t take long for me to realize that I was looking at an enormous cloud"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38867.0,
      "end_time": 40650.0,
      "text": "of air pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40994.0,
      "end_time": 44565.0,
      "text": "The contrast between the scenic environment I knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44589.0,
      "end_time": 46873.0,
      "text": "and this smog-covered skyline"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46898.0,
      "end_time": 48501.0,
      "text": "stirred up something within me."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49920.0,
      "end_time": 54568.0,
      "text": "I was appalled by the possibility of this city of bright and vivid sunsets"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54592.0,
      "end_time": 56726.0,
      "text": "being overrun by a dull haze."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57258.0,
      "end_time": 61262.0,
      "text": "At that moment, I felt an urge to do something about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61286.0,
      "end_time": 62942.0,
      "text": "but I didn&#39;t know what."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63808.0,
      "end_time": 66983.0,
      "text": "All I knew was I couldn&#39;t just stand idly by."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67564.0,
      "end_time": 69660.0,
      "text": "The main challenge was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69685.0,
      "end_time": 73922.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know much about environmental science"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73946.0,
      "end_time": 75471.0,
      "text": "air-quality management"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75495.0,
      "end_time": 76918.0,
      "text": "or atmospheric chemistry."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77827.0,
      "end_time": 79716.0,
      "text": "I am a computer engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79740.0,
      "end_time": 83759.0,
      "text": "and I was pretty sure I couldn&#39;t code my way out of this air pollution problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83783.0,
      "end_time": 84844.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84868.0,
      "end_time": 87399.0,
      "text": "Who was I to do anything about this issue?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87888.0,
      "end_time": 90432.0,
      "text": "I was but a citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91786.0,
      "end_time": 95667.0,
      "text": "In the following years, I learned a very important lesson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95691.0,
      "end_time": 99849.0,
      "text": "a lesson we all need to take to heart if we are to work towards a better future."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100738.0,
      "end_time": 104412.0,
      "text": "Even if you&#39;re not an expert in a particular domain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104436.0,
      "end_time": 107199.0,
      "text": "your outside expertise may hold the key"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107223.0,
      "end_time": 109818.0,
      "text": "to solving big problems within that domain."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110381.0,
      "end_time": 113730.0,
      "text": "Sometimes the unique perspective you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113970.0,
      "end_time": 117558.0,
      "text": "can result in unconventional thinking that can move the needle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117582.0,
      "end_time": 120982.0,
      "text": "but you need to be bold enough to try."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121752.0,
      "end_time": 123934.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the only way you&#39;ll ever know."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124889.0,
      "end_time": 126435.0,
      "text": "What I knew back then"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126459.0,
      "end_time": 130411.0,
      "text": "was that if I was even going to try to make a difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130435.0,
      "end_time": 133459.0,
      "text": "I had to get smart about air pollution first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133483.0,
      "end_time": 136578.0,
      "text": "and so I became a student again."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137522.0,
      "end_time": 139628.0,
      "text": "I did a bit of basic research"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139652.0,
      "end_time": 141652.0,
      "text": "and soon learned that air pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141676.0,
      "end_time": 144809.0,
      "text": "is the world&#39;s biggest environmental health risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145816.0,
      "end_time": 148190.0,
      "text": "Data from the World Health Organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148214.0,
      "end_time": 153356.0,
      "text": "shows that almost 14 percent of all deaths worldwide in 2012"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153380.0,
      "end_time": 157640.0,
      "text": "were attributable to household and ambient air pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157880.0,
      "end_time": 160547.0,
      "text": "with most occurring in low- and middle-income countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161449.0,
      "end_time": 165180.0,
      "text": "Ambient air pollution alone causes more deaths each year"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165204.0,
      "end_time": 167520.0,
      "text": "than malaria and HIV/AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168355.0,
      "end_time": 172188.0,
      "text": "In Africa, premature deaths from unsafe sanitation"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172212.0,
      "end_time": 173951.0,
      "text": "or childhood malnutrition"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173975.0,
      "end_time": 177515.0,
      "text": "pale in comparison to deaths due to air pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177539.0,
      "end_time": 180244.0,
      "text": "and it comes at a huge economic cost:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180269.0,
      "end_time": 184402.0,
      "text": "over 400 billion US dollars as of 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184426.0,
      "end_time": 189417.0,
      "text": "according to a study by the Organisation for Economic Cooperation and Development."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189862.0,
      "end_time": 192974.0,
      "text": "Now, in my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192998.0,
      "end_time": 197184.0,
      "text": "I explore new frontiers for artificial intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197208.0,
      "end_time": 200645.0,
      "text": "where the symbiotic relationship between man and machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 200669.0,
      "end_time": 204581.0,
      "text": "can find a beneficial footing and help us to make better decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205249.0,
      "end_time": 208313.0,
      "text": "As I thought about the air pollution problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208337.0,
      "end_time": 212283.0,
      "text": "it became clear that we needed to find a way to make better decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212307.0,
      "end_time": 214940.0,
      "text": "about how we manage air pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214964.0,
      "end_time": 216947.0,
      "text": "and given the scale of the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216971.0,
      "end_time": 219486.0,
      "text": "it was necessary to do it in a collaborative way."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 220310.0,
      "end_time": 224500.0,
      "text": "So I decided I&#39;d better get to know some people working within the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 225500.0,
      "end_time": 228922.0,
      "text": "I started to speak to officials from the City of Johannesburg"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228946.0,
      "end_time": 230573.0,
      "text": "and other surrounding cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 230597.0,
      "end_time": 233556.0,
      "text": "and I engaged the local scientific community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233580.0,
      "end_time": 235770.0,
      "text": "and I also made a few cold calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 237160.0,
      "end_time": 239569.0,
      "text": "The process of engagement I embarked upon"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 239593.0,
      "end_time": 242866.0,
      "text": "helped me to develop a deeper understanding of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 243510.0,
      "end_time": 245856.0,
      "text": "It also helped me to avoid the trap"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245880.0,
      "end_time": 249304.0,
      "text": "people in my profession sometimes fall into when trying to innovate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 249328.0,
      "end_time": 251655.0,
      "text": "where we are quick to apply a technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 251679.0,
      "end_time": 254473.0,
      "text": "before we&#39;ve firmly grasped the problem at hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255534.0,
      "end_time": 257671.0,
      "text": "I began to develop an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 257696.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260164.00000000003,
      "text": "about what I could do to improve the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260742.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263158.0,
      "text": "I started by simply asking myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263182.0,
      "end_time": 265880.0,
      "text": "how I could bring together in some meaningful way"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 265904.0,
      "end_time": 269772.0,
      "text": "my skills in software engineering and artificial intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 269796.0,
      "end_time": 272438.0,
      "text": "and the expertise of the people I&#39;d reached out to."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 273750.0,
      "end_time": 277680.0,
      "text": "I wanted to create an online air-quality management platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277920.0,
      "end_time": 279173.0,
      "text": "that would uncover trends in pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279197.0,
      "end_time": 281123.0,
      "text": "and project into the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 281147.0,
      "end_time": 283546.0,
      "text": "to determine what outcomes can be expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284462.0,
      "end_time": 289849.0,
      "text": "I was determined to see my idea translate into a practical solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 289874.0,
      "end_time": 292702.0,
      "text": "but I faced uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292726.0,
      "end_time": 294627.0,
      "text": "and had no guarantee of success."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295576.0,
      "end_time": 300894.0,
      "text": "What I had was a very particular set of engineering skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 300918.0,
      "end_time": 303354.0,
      "text": "skills I&#39;d acquired over my career"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 303378.0,
      "end_time": 304623.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304647.0,
      "end_time": 308109.0,
      "text": "that were new to people who had been working on the air pollution problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 308133.0,
      "end_time": 309650.0,
      "text": "for so many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 309675.0,
      "end_time": 314644.0,
      "text": "What I have come to realize is that sometimes just one fresh perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 314668.0,
      "end_time": 315961.0,
      "text": "one new skill set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 315985.0,
      "end_time": 319406.0,
      "text": "can make the conditions right for something remarkable to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 320660.0,
      "end_time": 323756.0,
      "text": "Our willpower and imagination are a guiding light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 323781.0,
      "end_time": 327518.0,
      "text": "enabling us to chart new paths and navigate through obstacles."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 328241.0,
      "end_time": 331899.0,
      "text": "Armed with a firmer understanding of the air pollution problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 331923.0,
      "end_time": 335285.0,
      "text": "and having managed to source over a decade&#39;s worth of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 335309.0,
      "end_time": 336761.0,
      "text": "on air pollutant levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 336785.0,
      "end_time": 341259.0,
      "text": "and the meteorological conditions for in and around Johannesburg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341283.0,
      "end_time": 345395.0,
      "text": "my colleagues from South Africa and China and myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345419.0,
      "end_time": 348156.0,
      "text": "created an air-quality decision support system"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 348180.0,
      "end_time": 349530.0,
      "text": "that lives in the cloud."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 350210.0,
      "end_time": 354281.0,
      "text": "This software system analyzes historical and real-time data"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354305.0,
      "end_time": 356973.0,
      "text": "to uncover the spatial-temporal trends in pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357695.0,
      "end_time": 360550.0,
      "text": "We then used new machine learning technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 360574.0,
      "end_time": 363213.0,
      "text": "to predict future levels of pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 363237.0,
      "end_time": 366134.0,
      "text": "for several different pollutants days in advance."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366849.0,
      "end_time": 370307.0,
      "text": "This means that citizens can make better decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 370331.0,
      "end_time": 372460.0,
      "text": "about their daily movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 372700.0,
      "end_time": 374850.0,
      "text": "and about where to settle their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 374575.0,
      "end_time": 378580.0,
      "text": "We can predict adverse pollution events ahead of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 378830.0,
      "end_time": 379884.0,
      "text": "identify heavy polluters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 379908.0,
      "end_time": 382431.0,
      "text": "and they can be ordered by the relevant authorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382455.0,
      "end_time": 384462.0,
      "text": "to scale back their operations."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385315.0,
      "end_time": 387830.0,
      "text": "Through assisted scenario planning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387854.0,
      "end_time": 390551.0,
      "text": "city planners can also make better decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390576.0,
      "end_time": 392581.0,
      "text": "about how to extend infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 392605.0,
      "end_time": 395392.0,
      "text": "such as human settlements or industrial zones."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 396160.0,
      "end_time": 398905.0,
      "text": "We completed a pilot of our technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398929.0,
      "end_time": 402256.0,
      "text": "that was run over a period of 120 days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402281.0,
      "end_time": 404456.0,
      "text": "covering all of South Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405376.0,
      "end_time": 407195.0,
      "text": "Our results were confirmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 407219.0,
      "end_time": 409782.0,
      "text": "when we demonstrated a tight correlation"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 409806.0,
      "end_time": 412203.0,
      "text": "between the forecasting data"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 412227.0,
      "end_time": 414822.0,
      "text": "and the data we were getting on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 415631.0,
      "end_time": 417301.0,
      "text": "Through our leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 417325.0,
      "end_time": 421174.0,
      "text": "we have brought cutting-edge, world-leading assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 421198.0,
      "end_time": 423864.0,
      "text": "that can perform air-quality forecasting"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 423888.0,
      "end_time": 428800.0,
      "text": "at an unprecedented resolution and accuracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 428320.0,
      "end_time": 434881.0,
      "text": "benefiting the city that I drove into one winter morning not very long ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 434905.0,
      "end_time": 436436.0,
      "text": "and thought to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 436460.0,
      "end_time": 439308.0,
      "text": "\"Something is wrong here. I wonder what can be done?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 440563.0,
      "end_time": 442904.0,
      "text": "So here is the point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 443895.0,
      "end_time": 447752.0,
      "text": "What if I&#39;d not investigated the problem of air pollution further?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 448951.0,
      "end_time": 452874.0,
      "text": "What if I&#39;d not shown some concern for the state of the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 452898.0,
      "end_time": 456874.0,
      "text": "and just hoped that someone, somewhere, was taking care of the matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 457858.0,
      "end_time": 459303.0,
      "text": "What I have learned is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 459327.0,
      "end_time": 461471.0,
      "text": "when embarking on a challenging endeavor"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 461495.0,
      "end_time": 464133.0,
      "text": "that advances a cause that we firmly believe in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 464157.0,
      "end_time": 467642.0,
      "text": "it is important to focus on the possibility of success"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 467666.0,
      "end_time": 470712.0,
      "text": "and consider the consequence of not acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 471426.0,
      "end_time": 475330.0,
      "text": "We should not get distracted by resistance and opposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 475355.0,
      "end_time": 477752.0,
      "text": "but this should motivate us further."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 478405.0,
      "end_time": 482912.0,
      "text": "So wherever you are in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 482936.0,
      "end_time": 484375.0,
      "text": "the next time you find"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 484399.0,
      "end_time": 486593.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s some natural curiosity you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 486617.0,
      "end_time": 488217.0,
      "text": "that is being piqued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 488241.0,
      "end_time": 490296.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s about something you care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 490320.0,
      "end_time": 493105.0,
      "text": "and you have some crazy or bold ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 493129.0,
      "end_time": 496793.0,
      "text": "and perhaps it&#39;s outside the realm of your expertise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 496817.0,
      "end_time": 498550.0,
      "text": "ask yourself this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 499278.0,
      "end_time": 500515.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 502349.0,
      "end_time": 504866.0,
      "text": "Why not just go ahead and tackle the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504890.0,
      "end_time": 507691.0,
      "text": "as best as you can, in your own way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 507715.0,
      "end_time": 509969.0,
      "text": "You may be pleasantly surprised."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 511640.0,
      "end_time": 512215.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 512239.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515888.00000000006,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}